@startuml
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam BoxPadding 10

box "Boundary: crates/ide" #F0F8FF
participant "LSP Handlers\n(goto_definition.rs)" as Handlers
participant "**ide::Analysis**\n(Facade Struct)" as Facade
end box

box "Internal Subsystems" #FFF5EE
participant "SourceDatabase\n(Salsa DB)" as DB
participant "Hir\n(Semantic)" as HIR
participant "Syntax\n(Parser)" as Syntax
end box

autonumber

Handlers -> Facade : Calls semantic method\n(goto_definition)
activate Facade

note right of Facade
  Acts as a Facade, hiding
  the underlying complexity 
  of queries and compilation layers.
end note

Facade -> DB : Request semantic data\nvia Salsa queries
activate DB

DB -> HIR : Invoke hir analysis
activate HIR

HIR -> Syntax : Parse syntax tree
activate Syntax
Syntax --> HIR : Return tree
deactivate Syntax

HIR --> DB : Return semantic info
deactivate HIR

DB --> Facade : Return raw data
deactivate DB

Facade --> Handlers : Return simplified LSP-ready result
deactivate Facade

@enduml